On June 30, the Tymiryazevsky District Court of Moscow sentenced Vasily Serosthanov to three years in the colony, and Anton Mamayev to four and a half years in prison with punishment in the colony of the general regime (per Art. 2 of Art. 162 of the Criminal Code of the Russian Federation).
